2 DNS Enumeration â€“ dnsrecon
Command Used
dnsrecon -d cepialabs.com -t std

Result
ERROR This type of scan is not valid

Reason

Incorrect scan type was supplied.

Correct Command
dnsrecon -d tesla.com -t std

Findings

SOA records discovered

Multiple authoritative NS (Name Server) records

BIND version leakage

DNSSEC enumeration attempt

Sample Output Evidence
SOA edns69.ultradns.com
NS a1-12.akam.net
Bind Version: 32068.140

Security Impact
Finding	Risk
Name Server Exposure	Helps attackers perform DNS brute-force & zone walking
BIND Version Leak	Enables version-specific vulnerability exploitation
DNSSEC misconfiguration	Enables spoofing & MITM opportunities
