Security Impact

Subdomains dramatically increase the attack surface.

Exposure Type	Security Risk
dev.*	Development systems exposed
staging.*	Pre-production vulnerabilities
api.*	API abuse & token leakage
test.*	Misconfigurations
admin.*	Privilege escalation
ğŸ”¥ Why Subdomains Matter for Attackers

Attackers use subdomain discovery to:

Locate hidden admin panels

Discover internal dashboards

Access testing servers

Find exposed APIs

Perform password spraying & brute-force attacks

